node.text:
↓↓↓ 
 
WORLDWIDE / GIVEAWAY

We give one @nikifilini hoodie to one random follower who fulfilled the simple conditions on all the following accounts:

TERMS👇

🌀 Follow @trendy.manga, @naruto.trendy, @trendy.anime

❣ Like on the giveaway post of each account

👺 Comment on the giveaway post of each account

In 5 days we will sum up the results and choose 1 WINNER » The 23 of September

Also we give daily prizes from @nikifilini for repost.

⚙ Every day we will randomly choose + 1 winner among those who repost in stories the giveaway post of @trendy.manga or @naruto.trendy or @trendy.anime » Choose your favourite public and repost it!

Try your luck!

#anime #manga #narutoshippuden #naruto #anime #manga #hoodie #hoodies #giveaway
